      "acceptanceCriteria": "Commercial CFD solver with documented QA process and version control meets MRL 2 requirements.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023R1 used under institutional software QA protocol; version-controlled input files archived in institutional repository. SQA documentation reviewed and confirmed compliant with MRL 2 expectations."
