      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver verified against published benchmark cases relevant to rotating machinery internal flow.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent has been verified against FDA benchmark nozzle and backward-facing step cases. Published verification reports from ANSYS and independent literature confirm solver correctness for laminar and turbulent internal flows at MRL 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
