      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation geometry, flow regime, and fluid properties are representative of CPB COU.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry operating in the CPB flow range (3–6 L/min, 2000–3500 RPM). Blood analog fluid used. Validation scenario assessed as sufficiently representative of the COU for MRL 2."
    },
    {
