    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed per ASME V&V 40 Table 4 for MRL 2. CFD model accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. RHI predictions within 15% of experimental measurements across all 5 operating points satisfies the RH < 1 acceptance criterion relative to predicate device.",
